                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "The tattoo casts  *harm* ,  *heal* , or the 1st-rank spell from your deity\u2019s cleric spells. You can choose  *harm* or  *heal* only in accord with the deity\u2019s divine font. If the deity allows either spell, choose one the tattoo can cast when you receive the tattoo. The DC for any of these spells is 18.",
